@startuml
title 04 - Tracking e Notificação - Fluxo Feliz

autonumber
participant "Carrier/Provider" as Provider
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Tracking Service" as Tracking
database "Tracking DB" as TrackingDb
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
database "Notification DB" as NotificationDb
actor Buyer as Comprador

Provider -> Kafka: CarrierTrackingEventIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> Tracking: Consome evento de tracking
activate Tracking
Tracking -> TrackingDb: Verifica inbox por messageId
Tracking -> TrackingDb: Verifica duplicidade providerEventId
Tracking -> TrackingDb: Persiste TrackingEvent
Tracking -> TrackingDb: Atualiza ShipmentTracking
Tracking -> Kafka: TrackingStatusChangedIntegrationEvent
deactivate Tracking

Kafka -> Notification: Consome TrackingStatusChangedIntegrationEvent
activate Notification
Notification -> NotificationDb: Verifica inbox por messageId
Notification -> NotificationDb: Carrega preferências do destinatário
Notification -> NotificationDb: Cria Notification + Delivery
Notification -> Provider: Envia mensagem no canal configurado
Provider --> Notification: Accepted
Notification -> NotificationDb: Marca delivery como Accepted
Notification -> Kafka: NotificationAcceptedIntegrationEvent
deactivate Notification

Notification --> Comprador: Recebe atualização de entrega

@enduml
